  {
    "hotel_id": "985386",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/oyo-146-solace-hotel/hotel/manila-ph.html",
    "name": "Solace Hotel",
    "detail": "We had a great 2 night stay at Solace Hotel in Makati and were definitely surprised by it. The location was great it's just a quick jeepney ride to our office. Although, there isn't much nice view outside. Bu, no biggie. I fell in love the moment I stepped in the reception area. The hotel is clean and stylish and the bedroom is well equipped and comfortable. I just wished they had a smoking room or at least a small smoking area on every floor (You have to go to the parking entrance to smoke) But no, not a big issue really. The service at the breakfast was fine, not very much food to choose from, but hey, it's still buffet and considering the price! The staffs are very friendly and pleasant. Note, this is not a 4/5-star hotel or so, but the atmosphere is so special that it really felt like home to me. All respect for the general manager who does a great job here; a true sample of excellent hospitality! Also, if I may add. I hope they have a pool. :) Note, this is not even a 5-star hotel, but the atmosphere is so special that it really felt like home to me. Would definitely recommend Solace Hotel! :) ",
