    "detail": "sea residence is good when it comes to amenities, cleanliness and very friendly staff of the condominium. downside is the lessor / or owner and the agent. the owner did not even bother to greet us even though she was introduced to us by the agent not even a smile (as far as i remember)... during signing of some papers at the lobby, the agent even ask us bayad na naman kayo sa agoda di ba? no blankets, we need to call the agent (not responding thru text messages) just to inform them that there are no blankets. towels, we're hang inside the cabinet that looks like it was already used and not changed.. do i have to mention here that the towel they bring us we're brought by a 6 0r 7 year old girl??? best part of our stay... check-out day, at exactly 12:00pm one lady knock thru the door, telling us that it's time to vacate the unit because somebody will check-in... again, no greetings! not even a single smile!!! then i told her, we're already fixing our things and in 5 minutes we will be out, she told us ok i'll just wait for you in the lobby when we go down in the lobby, we cannot find her! cellphone of the agent is off!!! we are very, very disappointed with the owner and agent of this unit. ",
